These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, iced-tea, milk, soy-milk
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: romance, mystery, comedy, action, spy
There are 5 different nationalities: american, japanese, italian, russian, colombian
5 different pets are kept: snake, turtle, horse, hamster, mouse
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 2. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 3. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the owner of the snake is the person watching romance movies##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 7. the american is on the left of the italian##1
 8. the person drinking milk is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 9. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking cola is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is between the japanese and the person watching spy movies##2
12. the russian is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
13. the colombian is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | cola        | mirinda | soy-milk     | iced-tea   | milk |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy     | mystery      | action | spy   | romance    |
| Nationality   | russian  | japanese     | american | italian | colombian  |
| Pet           | turtle | horse      | mouse     | hamster   | snake     |

