.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, video-games, magic-tricks, camping
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: electronic, house, trance, funk, hip-hop
There are 5 different nationalities: british, turkish, american, indonesian, argentine
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, airplane, jet-ski, motorbike, ship
 1. the person driving the ship is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the turkish##1
 5. the person driving the airplane is between the british and the fan of hip-hop##2
 6. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 8. the american is the fan of funk##1
 9. the american is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
10. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of house##1
11. the american is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
12. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | card-games | camping    | puzzles  | video-games    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | house       | trance      | electronic | funk        |
| Nationality   | argentine   | turkish     | british    | indonesian  | american     |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | airplane | ship | motorbike | bus |

