 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is the fan of salsa##1
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of hip-hop is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching action movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the fan of techno##1
 7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the fan of disco is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is climbing is the person watching animation movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
13. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person watching romance movies and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | baking | hiking     | chess   | drawing   | camping |
