 3. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
 4. the spanish is between the fan of pop and the person eating mango##2
 5. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 6. the fan of folk is on the right of the french##1
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is the fan of soul##1
 9. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
10. the fan of pop is the indian##1
11. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
12. the indian is on the right of the fan of house##1
13. the fan of soul is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
