.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, water, fanta, sprite
There 5 different types of food: zucchini, cauliflower, pineapple, pumpkin, peach
The people have 5 different jobs:  electrician, bartender, analyst, paramedic, police-officer
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: handball, cricket, skiing, water-polo, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the electrician##1
 2. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 4. the person drinking water is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person eating zucchini##2
 5. the person eating peach is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the bartender##1
 8. the police-officer is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the electrician##1
11. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
12. the paramedic is on the left of the electrician##1
13. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | fanta       | sprite       | soy-milk   | water      | hot-chocolate    |
| Food       | peach | pumpkin        | zucchini       | pineapple       | cauliflower |
| Job        | police-officer     | bartender        | paramedic | electrician        | analyst  |
| Sport      | water-polo | skiing | handball      | surfing | cricket  |

