 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the pakistani##1
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is between the person watching romance movies and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
 7. the person who's sport is golf is the egyptian##1
 8. the mexican is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the pakistani##1
10. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
11. the person watching action movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
12. the person drinking juice is on the right of the british##1
13. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1

