 2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 4. the owner of the fish is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the nigerian##2
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 6. the person who's hobby is video-games is in the middle##1
 7. the german is on the right of the chinese##1
 8. the malaysian is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the bird is the german##1
10. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
11. the owner of the bird is on the right of the chinese##1
12. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
13. the owner of the fish is on the left of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
