 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 7. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 9. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the ship is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's hobby is baking##2
12. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
13. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | cola       | tea    | hot-chocolate | fanta  | water        |
| Hobby       | magic-tricks | hiking | baking  | woodworking | rock-climbing    |
| Sport       | biathlon        | skiing   | soccer  | volleyball   | lacrosse |
| Transport   | taxi       | ship      | car      | roller | snowmobile  |

