.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, tea, soy-milk, mirinda
The people have 5 different jobs:  videographer, writer, accountant, designer, freelancer
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: satire, martial-arts, thriller, action, documentary
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: disco, reggae, country, soul, dubstep
 1. the fan of country is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 2. the designer is between the person watching thriller movies and the accountant##2
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is the designer##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 5. the person watching satire movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is between the freelancer and the fan of reggae##2
 7. the fan of soul is the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person drinking juice is the fan of country##1
 9. the fan of disco is on the left of the freelancer##1
10. the videographer is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
11. the accountant is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
12. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
