 4. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the rat is between the russian and the owner of the bird##2
 6. the russian is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person driving the van and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is boatd-games##2
 9. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who's hobby is boatd-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is boatd-games is on the right of the spanish##1

